â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   Purpose: Provides an optional sign-up point for users. Accessed directly after Index.tsx or after BusinessOverviewPage.tsx if user went back.
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   Details:
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   - Jungle theme, full-screen layout.
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚   - Sign up form and "Continue as Guest" option.
